{"tid":416769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微博招募千名監督員　舉報數量前十者或賞iPhone","createTime":"2017-09-28T05:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T05:38:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94189dfe8567bc5bcaca285eda9f37fbea57df5b","tid":416769,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170928/s00004/c3a665cb915f4f44d5a569397f11f83f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170928%2Fs00004%2Fc3a665cb915f4f44d5a569397f11f83f.jpg&h=24f8036e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新浪微博社區管理官方微博周三（27日）發布消息，公開招募1000名微博監督員，每月協助舉報不少於200條微博上的「涉黃、違法、有害」信息，舉報者除了可獲得200元補貼，以及專屬的「橙V」認證外，舉報數目最多的前十名可獲得蘋果手機、國產手機、筆記本電腦等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，監督員亦需要接受年終考核排名，排名靠前的將獲得年終獎勵並推薦為「首都互聯網協會網站優秀自律專員」。不過，監督員有退出機制，包括主動退出；對其他用戶進行惡意舉報、敲詐勒索等有損監督員形象行為；當月錯誤舉報超過3次，以及年終考核排名末尾等4種情況。<br />\n<br />\n日前，新浪微博因其用戶發布傳播「淫穢色情信息、宣揚民族仇恨信息及相關評論信息」等，被北京市網信辦批評「未盡到管理義務」。網信辦依據《中華人民共和國網絡安全法》，對新浪微博處以最高罰款決定，並要求微博作出整頓。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170928/s00004/1506573283680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170928%2Fs00004%2F1506573283680&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78feargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=4aa012af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170928%2Fs00004%2F1506573283680&h=1d78cd3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170928/s00004/1506573283680</a>"},{"pid":"1ad6a90413d52518cdfbaee11d9be4b2e94246f2","tid":416769,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"鄰國崛起點解唔送小米華為 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma